name: 7.92x57 Mauser S
description: The 7.92×57mm Mauser is a rimless bottlenecked rifle cartridge. The 7.92×57mm Mauser cartridge was adopted by the German Empire in 1903–1905, and was the German service cartridge in both World Wars.

name: 7.92x57mm casing
description: An empty casing from a 7.92x57 round.
